messages.messageBody:
Hi there,
My name is Govinda. I live in Visalia, Ca. and am looking for
others, in the Visalia area, with teenagers who are making the
transition to trying to find a job or go to collage. My boy is 18 and
is feeling anxious about his future. I would like to find some
friends in the area for both of us.
My boy's name is Keshava. He is very good musically with guitar
playing especially. He also has a keyboard, cello, and just recently
got a sitar. He loves to work on computer graphic and game making.
I have many interests, music, learning NVC, photography, cooking,
spiritual life. Our family is vegetarian.

Nice to be here,
Govinda
